{"tid":1417451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非，勇武，都是命運共同體。","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:52:00.000Z","uid":294142,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97653b239ce5c709d1afe1ea4d3db990dae4fb12","tid":1417451,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"經過今日，見到好多人話可以停一停勇武，試下和理非，唔好比人口實。<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地停止用二分法去判斷自己身份，黃藍，新舊香港人，廢青廢老，勇武和理非。政府，傳媒去形容大家時，大家只有一個身份，就係示威者，我地係命運共同體。<br />\n<br />\n就算我地行為唔同，唔化表我地係兩種唔同人，心肝脾肺腎都有唔同功能，但有其中一樣停止時，成個身體都會運作失常，甚至最後全部收皮，一命嗚呼。<br />\n<br />\n記住，今日我地出得來，就係同命相連，任何一邊背棄對方，最後都會殊途同歸。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔需要叫邊面暫停，只需要互相扶持。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4af24e68d24d1db254c767c557a24bac24954303","tid":1417451,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ad6b6401ebc61f69af2fbb709b93735c39d70b","tid":1417451,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4865991d2b5858747b57489dc443e8f1c177ab9","tid":1417451,"uid":150935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"依家叫勇武停，政府就會100%開始清算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417206</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8bc3e196b20e26e098dda9f7ca057fd1e837f730","tid":1417451,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ca9edf7309291656bede9641727c47ad9da2ac","tid":1417451,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hk